systemInfo.legalInformationSummary: Urubuga Irembo rwiyemeje kurinda ubusugire n'umutekano w'amakuru aranga abarukoresha. Twashyizeho ingamba n'amabwiriza ajyanye n'umutekano n'imikoreshereze ya serivisi dutanga binogeye abatugana.
systemInfo.termsOfUse:
Murakaza neza. Turabashimiye gusura Irembo, urubuga rutangirwaho serivisi za Leta ukoresheje ikoranabuhanga(e-gov). Nkuko bisanzwe ku zindi mbuga nyinshi, uru rubuga rufite amategeko agenga imikoreshereze na serivisi zirutangirwaho. Ayo mategeko, twise "amabwiriza ku mikoreshereze", akubiye mu masezerano ku mikoreshereze y’urubuga. Niba ukoresheje uru rubuga, wiyemeje gukurikiza no kutarenga ku mabwiriza akurikira. Banza uyasome neza. Niba hari ibyo utemeye muri aya mabwiriza, reka gukoresha uru rubuga.

Uru rubuga ni urwande, rukora rute?

Uru rubuga rukora nka sisitemu y'ikoranabuhanga itunganya uburyo bw’imitangire ya serivisi hagati y'Ibigo bya Leta n'abarukoresha; imikoreshereze n'imitunganyirize y'urwo rubuga ikaba igengwa n’Ikigo cyigenga aricyo Irembo Ltd gifitanye amasezerano y'imikoranire y'imyaka 25 na Leta y’u Rwanda.

Leta ifatanyije n'ibigo biyishamikiyeho ifite inshingano zo gutegura no gutunganya amakuru agomba gushyirwa ku rubuga no guha Ikigo Irembo amakuru yose akenewe kandi ajyanye n'igihe kugirango abakeneye serivisi babashe kuzihabwa.

Uburenganzira bukomye

Irembo n’ikirangantego cyaryo bikingiwe n'uburenganzira bukomye bw’Ikigo Irembo Ltd, bikazasubizwa Leta aya masezerano arangiye.

Kwiyandikisha

Dushobora kugusaba gufungura konti ku rubuga Irembo kugirango ushobore kubona zimwe muri serivisi zirutangirwaho ariko ibi si ngombwa igihe ukoresha sisitemu ya USSD *909#.

Inshingano z'ukoresha urubuga

Ugomba gukoresha urubuga www.irembo.gov.rw na konti yawe ku mpanvu zubahiriza amategeko no mu buryo butabangamira undi muntu mu bijyanye n’uburenganzira bw'imikoreshereze n'ubwisanzure ku rubuga.

Uburenganzira bwo guhindura amabwiriza ku mikoreshereze y’Urubuga

Irembo rishobora kuvugurura amabwiriza ku mikoreshereze y’Urubuga igihe bibaye ngombwa. Iyo ivugurura ribaye, ibyavuguruwe nibyo bishyirwa ku rubuga. Turabamenyesha ko impinduka zikurikizwa iyo zamaze gushyirwa ku rubuga, musabwe rero guhora musoma ibiri ku rubuga kugirango mumenye ko hari impinduka zabaye. Igihe bibaye ngombwa, urubuga rwoherereza email cyangwa SMS uwiyandikishije rukamumenyesha impinduka zabaye.

Igihe ukomeje gukoresha urubuga Irembo nyuma y'uko impinduka zatangiye gukurikizwa, uba wiyemeje kubahiriza ayo mabwiriza yavuguruwe.

Kubahiriza amabwiriza

Urubuga Irembo ruhora rugenzura ko amabwiriza kubarukoresha yubahirizwa. Rwubahiriza n'andi mabwiriza agenga imikorere yarwo. Rukorana kandi n'ibindi bigo ngengamikorere hagamijwe gukemura ibibazo bishingiye ku makuru aranga abarukoresha rudashobora kwikemurira ubwarwo.
systemInfo.disclaimer:
Amabwiriza ku bakoresha Urubuga Irembo

Abakoresha urubuga Irembo bose basabwa kubanza gusoma aya mabwiriza mbere yo kurukoresha kugirango babashe gusobanukirwa neza ibyo batagomba kurengaho n'inshingano z’Irembo zirebana n'ibivugwa muri iyi nyandiko.

Icyitonderwa muri rusange

Urubuga Irembo rwitwararika mu gushyira ku rubuga amakuru yizewe aturutse mu nzego za Leta zitandukanye ariko ntirushobora kwirengera amakosa, ibyibagiranye, cyangwa ingaruka zaterwa n'imikoreshereze y'ayo makuru.

Urubuga Irembo n'izindi mbuga

Urubuga Irembo ruhuzwa n’izindi sisitemu z’imbuga za Leta n’izibindi bigo biyishamikiyeho zidakontororwa n’Irembo. Ntabwo rero tugenga imiterere y'izo mbuga, ibizirimo ndetse n'uburyo zikora.

Ihuzwa ry' urubuga Irembo n'izindi mbuga za Leta bikorwa kugirango umuntu abashe kugera ku bikubiye muri izo mbuga ariko ntibivuga ko twishingiye amakuru aziriho.

Kwishyura

Kwishyura serivisi ku rubuga Irembo bishobora gukorwa hifashishijwe uburyo butandukanye aribwo telefoni igendanwa, ikarita yo kubitsa no kubikuza, na mVisa n'andi makarita akoreshwa mu ma banki dukorana. Umuyoboro wo kwishyura ukoresheje interineti washyizweho kugirango kwishyura serivisi bikorwe mu buryo bworoshye utagombye kujya kuri banki. Irembo ntirizigera ribazwa imikoreshereze mibi y'uwo muyoboro. Ugomba kumenya neza ko ibijyanye n'imyishyurire kuri interineti ari wowe bireba na banki mukorana gusa.

Amakuru ari ku ikarita yo kubitsa no kubikuza watanze kugirango ubashe gukoresha umuyoboro wo kwishyura agomba kuba atunganye, ari ukuri kandi ntugomba gukoresha ikarita utabonye mu buryo bwemewe n’amategeko.

Igihe ukoresheje urubuga Irembo wishyura serivisi, urubuga rusigarana inyandiko zerekana uwasabye iyo serivisi, igihe yayisabiye, umubare w’amafaranga yishyuye n’uburyo yakoreheje yishyura ariko ntiruzagumana nomero yawe ya PIN cyangwa ijambo ry’ibanga byakoreshejwe na sistemu zo kwishyura keretse ubitangiye uburenganzira mu nyandiko.

Gusubizwa amafaranga

Iyo Irembo rigejejweho ikibazo cyo gusubiza amafaranga rigasanga gifite ishingiro (cyangwa se gusubiza amafaranga uwasabye serivisi bikaba bikurikije amategeko akoreshwa), ryihutira gusubiza ayo mafaranga.

Nk'uko amategeko abiteganya, ibyo Irembo hamwe n'abafatanyabikorwa baryo basabwa bireba gusa umubare w'amafaranga yishyuwe serivisi (cyangwa se kongera guha serivisi uwayisabye bundi bushya).

Abafatanyabikorwa

Irembo rikorana n'ibigo binyuranye kugirango ribashe gutanga serivisi. Muri byo twavuga ibirihagarariye, ibitanga serivisi za interineti, n’amabanki. Usaba serivisi nta mafaranga y'ikirenga asabwa uretse ayagenwe kandi agaragara ku rubuga, kandi Irembo ntiribazwa imikoreshereze mibi, ibyatakaye cyangwa ibyangiritse, ibyangiritse mu buryo budasanzwe, bufite ingaruka, bugaragara cyangwa buhanirwa bitewe cyangwa bifitanye isano n'abafatanyabikorwa bacu. Ibi bisobanura neza aho inshingano zacu zigarukira ku byerekeye ibyangiritse byose harimo (ariko bitagarukira gusa) ku ngurane y' ibyangijwe mu buryo butaziguye, buziguye cyangwa bishobora kugira ingaruka, gutakaza amakuru, umutungo cyangwa inyungu, gutakaza cyangwa kwangirika k'umutungo n'ibindi abafatanyabikorwa bacu bashobora kwishyuza.

Kwirinda Virusi

Irembo rikora ibishoboka byose kugirango rigenzure kandi risuzume ibishyirwa ku rubuga ku nzego zose zo kubaka urubuga rwa interineti Leta itangiraho serivisi. Abakoresha urubuga Irembo bakwiye gukoresha porogaramu zo kwirinda virusi igihe bakoresha inyandiko bakuye kuri interineti.

Irembo ntirishobora kubazwa na rimwe ibyabuze, ibitagenda, cyangwa ibyangiritse birebana n'amakuru cyangwa sisitemu yawe igihe ukoresha ibyavuye kuri uru rubuga cyangwa izindi mbuga za Leta.

Dufata ingamba zihamye zidufasha gucunga umutekano w’amakuru dukusanyije, tukayabika mu ibanga, kandi agahorana ubusugire. Muri izo ngamba harimo uburyo bwo kurinda amakuru ari ku rubuga kugirango atabonwa n'utabifitiye uburenganzira, bityo tugashobora kuzuza inshingano zacu.

Dukoresha kandi n'ubundi buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga budufasha gucunga umutekano w'amakuru abitswe ku rubuga.

Amategeko akurikizwa

Aya mabwiriza n'izindi nshingano zidakubiye mu masezerano zituruka cyangwa zifitanye isano nayo bigengwa kandi bisobanurwa n'amategeko y'u Rwanda. Ibitazunvikanwaho bijyanye cyangwa birurutse kuri aya mabwiriza no ku zindi nshingano zidakubiye mu masezerano bizakemurwa n'inkiko z'u Rwanda.
systemInfo.privacyStatementTitle: Amabwiriza ajyanye n'amakuru aranga abakoresha urubuga
systemInfo.privacyStatement:
Amakuru aranga abakoresha Urubuga

Aya mabwiriza agamije kubasobanurira uko urubuga Irembo rukoresha rukanarinda amakuru aranga abarukoresha. Kugirango dusobanukirwe neza aya mabwiriza, ayo makuru yahawe inyito “y' amakuru aranga abakoresha urubuga”, bikaba byubahirije Itegeko Nshinga rya Repubulika y'u Rwanda ryo mu 2015 nk'uko ryavuguruwe kugeza ubu (ingingo ya 23) rivuga ko imibereho bwite y'umuntu idashobora kuvogerwa.

Urubuga Irembo rutangirwaho serivisi za interineti ntirukoreshwa mu buryo bubonetse bwose. Ntabwo kandi rwiha amakuru aranga urukoresha, keretse iyo ayatanze kubushake.

Imikoreshereze y' amakuru urubuga Irembo rwakiriye

Muri rusange, urubuga Irembo ntirubika amakuru akuranga iyo urusuye, keretse ari wowe ubishatse. Gutanga amakuru akuranga ku rubuga bikorwa ku bushake. Iyo ubikoze, uba uduhaye uburenganzira bwo kuyakoresha kugirango uhabwe serivisi wifuza.

Urubuga irembo rwakira amakuru akuranga kugirango rugufashe kubona serivisi wifuza, harimo na serivisi zitangwa n'abandi bafatanyabikorwa bacu. Ayo makuru urubuga rushobora kuyahererekanya na Minisiteri n'ibigo bya Leta mu rwego rwo kuzuza inshingano zabyo no guha abaturage serivisi bifuza

Gutanga amakuru atari yo cyangwa y'ibinyoma uyanyujije ku rubuga www.irembo.gov.rw bifatwa kimwe no gutanga amakuru y'ibinyoma kw’ifishi cyangwa kuyatanga ubwawe kandi bishobora gutuma twanga kuguha serivisi, gukurikiranwa n'amategeko cyangwa guhanishwa gutanga ihazabu mu butabera.

Urubuga Irembo ntabwo rugurisha cyangwa ngo ruhe undi muntu amakuru ayo ariyo yose aranga urukoresha (yaba ukorera Leta cyangwa uwikorera)

Amakuru yose yatanzwe ku rubuga Irembo arindwa gutakara, gukoreshwa nabi, kubonwa cyangwa gutangazwa n'utabyemerewe, guhindurwa cyangwa kwangizwa

Imicungire y'amakuru asigara nyuma yo gusura urubuga

Amakuru asigara nyuma yo gusura urubuga ni amakuru yoherezwa na mugabuzi y'urubuga akabikwa muri mudasobwa y'urukoresha, kugirango azabashe kuyabona igihe ayakeneye cyangwa akaba yakoreshwa n'izindi mugabuzi. Amakuru asigara nyuma yo gusura urubuga, atuma ubasha kumenya amakuru ajyanye n'umwirondoro w'uwarusuye. Urubuga Irembo ntabwo rukoresha amakuru asigara kuri mudasobwa y'abarusuye rugamije kumenya imyirondoro yabo.

Ubusanzwe, amakuru asigara nyuma yo gusura urubuga agira ikimenyetso kigaragaza ko atekanye. Yitwa ko atekanye iyo yanditswe mu buryo bwa tekiniki buhisha imisomere yayo. Niba bigaragara ko ayo makuru adatekanye azoherezwa mu buryo bwa tekinike bwo guhisha imisomere yayo. Ayo makuru adatekanye aherekezwa n'uburyo bwihariye bufasha kuyasoma. Icyo abakoresha urubuga Irembo bagomba kumenya ni uko muri rusange amashusho yagenewe umutekano wayo.

Urubuga Irembo rwubatse ku buryo rudasigarana amakuru ajyanye n'imari y'urukoresha atabitangiye uburenganzira bwanditse.

Urubuga Irembo nirugusaba gutanga amakuru akuranga, ruzakumenyesha impamvu zihariye zitumye ruyagusaba, icyo ruzayakoresha n'impamvu ruzayamenyekanisha. Ayo makuru yose ntabwo ruyabika igihe kirenze icyateganyijwe, akurwaho iyo icyari kigamijwe cyakozwe. Ingamba nyazo zo gucunga umutekano w'amakuru zarafashwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda gutakaza, gukoresha nabi no kwangiza amakuru aranga ukoresha urubuga Irembo.
